---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'healthcare-system', text: 'Healthcare System', level: 2 },
  { id: 'visa-requirements', text: 'Visa Options', level: 2 },
  { id: 'insurance-requirements', text: 'Insurance Requirements', level: 2 },
  { id: 'recommended-providers', text: 'Recommended Providers', level: 2 },
  { id: 'costs', text: 'Expected Costs', level: 2 },
  { id: 'scenarios', text: 'Real-World Scenarios', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'Common Questions', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Timor-Leste Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/timor-leste/insurance' },
  { title: 'Insurance for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors' },
  { title: 'Indonesia for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/indonesia' },
  { title: 'Australia for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/australia' },
  { title: 'Portugal for Seniors', href: '/insurance-for/seniors/in/portugal' },
];

const providerColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'entryAge', header: 'Max Entry Age' },
  { key: 'renewal', header: 'Renewal' },
  { key: 'monthlyFrom', header: 'From (65-69)' },
  { key: 'timorFit', header: 'Timor Fit' },
];

const providerRows = [
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: '$450-645/mo', timorFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'BUPA Global', entryAge: '79', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: '$525-750/mo', timorFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'Allianz Care', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: '$405-580/mo', timorFit: 'Essential' },
  { provider: 'Now Health', entryAge: '74', renewal: 'Lifetime', monthlyFrom: '$375-535/mo', timorFit: 'Good' },
];

const costColumns = [
  { key: 'category', header: 'Expense' },
  { key: 'monthly', header: 'Monthly' },
  { key: 'annual', header: 'Annual' },
];

const costRows = [
  { category: 'International Insurance (65-69)', monthly: '$405-645', annual: '$4,860-7,740' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (70-74)', monthly: '$555-860', annual: '$6,660-10,320' },
  { category: 'International Insurance (75-79)', monthly: '$745-1,155', annual: '$8,940-13,860' },
  { category: 'Local Clinic Visit', monthly: '$30-80/visit', annual: 'Very affordable' },
  { category: 'Evacuation to Darwin/Singapore', monthly: 'N/A', annual: '$30,000-100,000' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Health Insurance for Seniors in Timor-Leste 2026 | Retirement Guide"
  description="Guide to health insurance for seniors in Timor-Leste. New nation, Portuguese influence, dive sites, and coverage for adventurous retirees 65+."
  headline="Health Insurance for Seniors in Timor-Leste"
  subheadline="Timor-Leste (East Timor) offers new nation adventure, Portuguese colonial heritage, untouched dive sites, mountain coffee country, and frontier experience—one of world's youngest countries for pioneering retirees."
  heroImage="/images/countries/timor-leste-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Senior Plans →"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/cigna-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Why Seniors Choose Timor-Leste</h2>
  <p>
    Timor-Leste (East Timor) offers frontier adventure in one of world's youngest nations (independent 2002). Portuguese colonial heritage with Catholic culture, untouched dive sites, coffee highlands, and raw authenticity. For pioneering retirees seeking truly off-beaten-path experience, Timor-Leste provides unique frontier appeal.
  </p>

  <p>
    Dili is the capital with most services. Baucau offers colonial architecture. Atauro Island has diving. Coffee highlands inland. Population ~1.3 million. Darwin, Australia is 1 hour flight; Singapore 3 hours—both provide medical backup.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-3">Key Facts for Seniors</h3>
    <ul class="text-primary-800 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Very limited; Darwin/Singapore evacuation</li>
      <li><strong>Language:</strong> Tetun, Portuguese; some Indonesian</li>
      <li><strong>Cost of Living:</strong> $800-1,500/month (USD); affordable but limited</li>
      <li><strong>Climate:</strong> Tropical; dry/wet seasons</li>
      <li><strong>Character:</strong> Frontier; developing; pioneering</li>
      <li><strong>Currency:</strong> US Dollar</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="healthcare-system">Timor-Leste Healthcare System</h2>
  <p>
    Timor-Leste healthcare is very limited—Hospital Nacional Guido Valadares in Dili is main facility but basic. Limited equipment and specialists. Some NGO clinics provide care. Complex cases require evacuation to Darwin, Australia (1 hour) or Singapore (3 hours). Healthcare infrastructure still developing after independence.
  </p>

  <p>
    Darwin provides closest quality backup—Royal Darwin Hospital. Singapore offers excellent options. International insurance with strong evacuation coverage absolutely essential.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-2">Darwin/Singapore Evacuation Essential</h3>
    <p class="text-amber-800 mb-0">
      Darwin is just 1 hour away with Australian healthcare standards. Singapore is 3 hours with world-class hospitals. Timor-Leste cannot treat most complex conditions. Insurance with Australia/Singapore coverage is non-negotiable.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="visa-requirements">Visa Options for Seniors</h2>
  <p>
    Timor-Leste visa options:
  </p>

  <h3>Visa on Arrival</h3>
  <p>
    30 days for many nationalities. $30 USD fee. Simple entry.
  </p>

  <h3>Visa Extension</h3>
  <p>
    Extensions available through Immigration. Various categories for longer stays.
  </p>

  <h3>Residence Visa</h3>
  <p>
    For long-term residence. Various categories. Apply through Immigration. Developing bureaucracy—patience required.
  </p>

  <h2 id="insurance-requirements">Insurance Requirements</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance requirements for Timor-Leste:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Entry:</strong> Travel insurance strongly recommended</li>
    <li><strong>Extended stay:</strong> International coverage essential</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation:</strong> Darwin and Singapore coverage critical</li>
    <li><strong>Diving:</strong> Diving insurance if participating</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Insurance Strategy for Timor-Leste</h3>
    <p class="text-blue-800 mb-0">
      Comprehensive international insurance with Darwin and Singapore evacuation absolutely essential. Local care handles only basic needs. Include diving coverage if exploring underwater sites. Don't underestimate healthcare limitations.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2 id="recommended-providers">Recommended Insurance Providers</h2>
  <p>
    For seniors in Timor-Leste, evacuation coverage critical:
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={providerColumns} rows={providerRows} />

  <h3>Why These Providers Work for Timor-Leste</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cigna Global:</strong> Strong Asia-Pacific network</li>
    <li><strong>BUPA Global:</strong> Highest entry age (79), comprehensive</li>
    <li><strong>Darwin access:</strong> Australian healthcare 1 hour away</li>
    <li><strong>Singapore backup:</strong> World-class 3 hours away</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Get Personalized Senior Quotes</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Compare coverage for Timor-Leste with regional evacuation.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
      <a href="/go/bupa-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get BUPA Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="costs">Expected Insurance Costs</h2>
  <p>
    Insurance costs for Timor-Leste (uses USD):
  </p>

  <ComparisonTable columns={costColumns} rows={costRows} />

  <h3>Cost Considerations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Low living costs:</strong> Very affordable daily expenses</li>
    <li><strong>Insurance matters:</strong> Don't skimp on evacuation</li>
    <li><strong>Limited supplies:</strong> Some items hard to find</li>
    <li><strong>USD economy:</strong> No currency exchange needed</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="scenarios">Real-World Scenarios</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 1: Portuguese Speaker, 66</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $1,800/month. Portuguese language advantage. Dili based.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Cigna Global with Asia-Pacific coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~$450/month. Language ease; Darwin backup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 2: Dive Enthusiast, 68</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $2,200/month. Atauro Island diving. Adventure focus.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> BUPA Global with diving coverage.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~$550/month. Untouched reefs; comprehensive backup.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Scenario 3: Aid Worker Retiree, 65</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Situation:</strong> $1,500/month. Former NGO. Development interest.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-2"><strong>Solution:</strong> Allianz Care with evacuation focus.</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0"><strong>Cost:</strong> ~$420/month. Meaningful connection; essential coverage.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="faqs">Common Questions</h2>

  <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is Timor-Leste suitable for seniors?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Only for adventurous pioneers—very limited healthcare, developing infrastructure, basic services. Not for those needing regular medical care or comfortable amenities. For hardy adventurers seeking frontier experience.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">What language do I need?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Portuguese helpful—official language with Tetun. Indonesian widely understood (former occupier). English limited but growing. Portuguese speakers have significant advantage. Learning basic Tetun appreciated locally.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Why would a senior choose Timor-Leste?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Unique frontier experience—one of world's youngest nations, untouched dive sites, Portuguese Catholic heritage, off-beaten-path adventure. Not for comfort; for pioneering spirits seeking somewhere truly different.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-b border-neutral-200 pb-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Is Timor-Leste safe?</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-0">
        Generally safe now—violent conflict ended 2006. Political stability improved. Petty crime exists but violent crime against foreigners rare. Roads can be dangerous. Normal developing country precautions apply.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Ready to Compare Options?</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Get quotes from providers for Timor-Leste coverage.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/go/cigna-global" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-primary-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Cigna Quote</a>
      <a href="/go/allianz-care" class="inline-block px-5 py-2.5 bg-neutral-700 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-800 transition-colors font-medium" style="color: white !important;">Get Allianz Quote</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-0">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Timor-Leste is a frontier destination with very limited healthcare. Evacuation coverage essential. Not suitable for most seniors. Only for adventurous pioneers willing to accept significant limitations.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
